dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This dataset contain the 7 Statistical Areas including General FMAs.
Data supply - extraneous attributes. There are some extra system ones. There is nothing that “needs” to be removed unless you want to make it tidier, Then remove Feature key, Layer key, Layer Group key, Metadata key. The portalurl is a link to metadata on AGOL which might be handy.
For more information please see NABIS: Freshwater Eel Statistical Areas http://www.nabis.govt.nz/LayerDetails.aspx?layer=Freshwater%20Eel%20Statistical%20Areas General Statistical Areas http://www.nabis.govt.nz/LayerDetails.aspx?layer=General%20Statistical%20Areas Inshore Statistical Areas http://www.nabis.govt.nz/LayerDetails.aspx?layer=Inshore%20Statistical%20Areas Oyster Statistical Areas http://www.nabis.govt.nz/LayerDetails.aspx?layer=Oyster%20Statistical%20Areas Paua Statistical Areas http://www.nabis.govt.nz/LayerDetails.aspx?layer=Paua%20Statistical%20Areas Rock Lobster Statistical Areas http://www.nabis.govt.nz/LayerDetails.aspx?layer=Rock%20lobster%20Statistical%20Areas Scallop Statistical Areas http://www.nabis.govt.nz/LayerDetails.aspx?layer=Scallop%20Statistical%20Areas
